           Dog.Breed breed)
        This constructs a cat with adoption data
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the dog
        birthday - The dogs birthday as a Date
        size - Size of the dog
        houseTrained - Boolean for if the dog is House trained or not
        goodWithKids - Boolean for if the dog is good with kids
        notes - All of the dogs notes
        dateEnterRescue - Date that the dog entered the rescue
        adopted - Boolean for if the dog is adopted
        dateAdopted - Date that the dog was adopted, null if cat isn't adopted
        owner - The dogs owner's name
        breed - Breed of the dog
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any of the following are true: name is null name is whitespace only name contains \n or , birthday is null size is null notes is null dateEnterRescue is null dateEnterRescue is before birthday adopted is false but dateAdopted or owner is non-null adopted is true but dateAdopted or owner is null dateAdopted is before dateEnterRescue owner is whitespace only owner contains \n or ,
